<pre>
1. Function Statement
: y = f(x)
: output = f(input)
: return multiple variable (keep them in order)
: don't hove to specify return type
: One line function is called lambda function
- def name(parameters) :
    statements            -&gt; í•¨ìˆ˜ë‚´ìš©
    return val1, val2 ... -&gt; ê²°ê³¼ë¬¼
</pre>
</body>
